 Pictured is Coderdojo Co Founder James Whelton and Megan Cowan (10). / Pictured is Coderdojo Co Founder James Whelton and Megan Cowan (10) Whelton is the founder of computer club and runaway success Coderdojo. From its humble beginnings in 2011 as an after-school meeting teaching HTML and CSS expand at Presentation Brothers College in Cork, Coderdojo clubs now take place around the world - as far as Panama, Bolivia, South Africa and Brazil. * Chupi Sweetman-Pell (30) Jewellery 





 
